features: 【Diaper Bag with Foldable Changing Station】This diaper bag backpack comes with a detachable changing station. 【Super Large Capacity】 Size 19.5x12.8x9.2 inches, 2.8 pounds. Fifteen pockets with super large capacity, two main pockets, and thirteen functional pockets can meet all the needs of mothers, storing bottles, clothes, towels, underwear, and diapers separately. Pockets with different functions will help you organize various items neatly.

【Portable with wide straps and stroller-hooks】This gray baby bag with a back three-dimensional ventilation design help for ventilation and heat elimination. Comfortable wide breathable mesh shoulder straps with plentiful sponge pad help relieve the stress from your shoulder. Lock buckle reduces the pressure on the palm when you handle it. 【Comfortable & Durable & Waterproof】The surface of the diaper bag is made of high-quality waterproof oxford cloth which is anti-wear and anti-dirt. the smooth zipper is convenient for you to open and close. Padded shoulder straps make the bag very comfortable to wear.

【Well made & All in One】We are a factory with 20 years of experience in making backpacks. A strict quality inspection ensures that every backpack is well-made. Ideal uses as Diaper Bag, Mommy Backpack, or Travel Bag. Unisex design makes it right for boys or girls. It is also a good choice as a baby shower gift.
